file.name: common-types.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.2"
info:
  version: 15.3.0
  title: "Common Data Types"
paths: {}
components:
  schemas:
    PetsList:
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/Pet'

    Pet:
      type: object
      properties:
        petType:
          type: string
        breed:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Breed'

    Breed:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        family:
          type: string
